  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Maximizing Livelihood Opportunities in Rural Communities: Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of training in planning and management to local district level authorities; Provision of training in sustainable agriculture practices,&#xA0;natural resource management, local development planning processes, and legislation to NSAs; Vocational training in food processing and packaging, marketing and business development and management to rural farmers, technical support to government agricultural extension services; Support to and training of district level DRR platforms; Advocacy; Technical and management training of CSOs; Facilitating meetings between local people, CSOs and local authorities; Exchange visits between local authorities/NSAs; Construction of seed and food stores.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To contribute to the achievement of MDG1 and food security in Burundi, Ethiopia and Tanzania</narrative>
